<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verifikasi - EzheGheler</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-base: #050507;
            --primary: #4f46e5;
            --secondary: #ec4899;
            --surface: rgba(20, 20, 25, 0.6);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #a1a1aa;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-base);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
        }

        .ambient-bg {
            position: fixed;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(120px);
            animation: float 15s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .orb-1 {
            width: 45vw;
            height: 45vw;
            background: var(--primary);
            top: -10vw;
            left: -10vw;
        }

        .orb-2 {
            width: 35vw;
            height: 35vw;
            background: var(--secondary);
            bottom: -10vw;
            right: 10vw;
            animation-delay: -5s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translate(5vw, 10vh);
            }
        }


        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .info-side {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 60px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.9) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 7, 0.4) 100%);
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .brand-logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .brand-logo i {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        .info-side h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #a1a1aa);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .info-side p.lead {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 16px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .feature-text h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .feature-text p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .login-side {
            width: 500px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .login-card {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--surface);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 55px 45px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: left;
            animation: slideLeft 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(30px);
        }

        @keyframes slideLeft {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .login-card h2 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .login-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 0 0 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-wrapper i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 16px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 14px 14px 45px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-family: 'Outfit';
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.15);
        }

        input:focus+i {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #3730a3);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Outfit';
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
        }

        .error-msg {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            color: #fca5a5;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .live-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
            color: #34d399;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .pulse-dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: #34d399;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #34d399;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0.95);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1.5);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                margin: 20px;
                height: auto;
            }

            .info-side {
                border-right: none;
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
                padding: 40px;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="ambient-bg">
        <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-2"></div>

    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Left Side -->
        <div class="info-side">
            <div class="brand-logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> EzheGheler Platform</div>

            <div class="live-badge">
                <div class="pulse-dot"></div> Node.js Server Aktif
            </div>

            <h1>Advanced Socket<br>Programming</h1>
            <p class="lead">Implementasi arsitektur jaringan berbasis klien-server. Sistem ini menggabungkan integritas
                data dari protokol TCP dan kecepatan transmisi dari protokol UDP.</p>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h4>Real-time Email Verification</h4>
                        <p>Autentikasi terintegrasi langsung dengan SMTP (Nodemailer) yang mengirim log email seketika
                            saat sesi dimulai.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-export"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h4>TCP File Transfer</h4>
                        <p>Penyaluran berkas biner secara andal (reliable) melintasi socket TCP khusus (Port 3001) antar
                            jaringan Klien-Server.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"
                        style="color: var(--secondary); background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1); border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish"></i></div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h4>UDP Media Broadcasting</h4>
                        <p>Distribusi potongan aliran media video langsung dengan kecepatan maksimal menggunakan soket
                            datagram (Port 4000).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side -->
        <div class="login-side">
            <div class="login-card">
                <h2>Verifikasi Login 2FA</h2>
                <p>Kami telah mengirimkan OTP 6 digit ke email Anda. Masukkan kode tersebut untuk masuk ke sistem.</p>

                <% if (typeof error !=='undefined' && error) { %>
                    <div class="error-msg">
                        <%= error %>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                        <form action="/verify" method="POST">
                            <input type="hidden" name="email" value="<%= email %>">

                            <div class="input-group">
                                <label for="code">Kode Verifikasi</label>
                                <div class="input-wrapper">
                                    <input type="text" id="code" name="code" required
                                        placeholder="Contoh: 123456" maxlength="6" style="text-align: center; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 5px;">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-key"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <button type="submit">
                                Verifikasi & Masuk Dashboard <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i>
                            </button>
                            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px;">
                                Salah email? <a href="/" style="color: var(--secondary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Kembali ke Login</a>
                            </p>
                        </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>